{"tid":2230520,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"立場： kenzo 創辦人高田賢三感染武肺於巴黎病逝","createTime":"2020-10-05T03:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T03:55:23.000Z","uid":140956,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f86680de44d6061ddc8de798e8042b6abbe8c580","tid":2230520,"uid":140956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"日本時裝品牌 Kenzo 創辦人高田賢三 ( Kenzo Takada )，因感染武漢肺炎在巴黎病逝，終年 81 歲。<br />\n<br />\n高田賢三於當地時間周日在巴黎美國醫院（American Hospital of Paris）去世。1939 年出生的高田賢三是首位在巴黎時裝界闖出名堂的日本設計師，於 1960 年代已移居巴黎，他以鮮艷色彩及喜用大自然花鳥、蝴蝶、動物圖案見稱。<br />\n<br />\n高田賢三於 1999 年宣布退休，將他的時裝店交予他的助手管理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65c9cc773409dfa9794858790fd4a318d67ca94","tid":2230520,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"之前sergio rossi 都係武肺死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16343363b70996a68cebbc93558a831c736b6ab","tid":2230520,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c65c9cc773409dfa9794858790fd4a318d67ca94","tid":2230520,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"之前sergio rossi 都係武肺死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"燕 knows well<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8941c969f3ee70c05b5d00c0892eb40503ac48","tid":2230520,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f16343363b70996a68cebbc93558a831c736b6ab","tid":2230520,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c65c9cc773409dfa9794858790fd4a318d67ca94","tid":2230520,"uid":34079